social_posts.post_text: Thought this would take a weekend… in October 😂

Had a blast learning from everyone at the continuing ed intensive at Paradigm Studio! I decided to throw myself into the world of classical Pilates for the first time 😅 

It was both fun and challenging, and amazing to watch truly advanced level athletes move! Returning home both grateful and stuffed with new things to  work into practice. Who knew footwork could be so hard?! Thank you @katie.yip !
Apparently there’s a nice view back there 🙃☁️
Well worth the 11,000km trip 🎉 Congratulations Mr. and Mrs. Cook! @rachbryant_

Did you know that foam rollers can be used for more than just myofascial release? Here are some clips of a full body stability based workout plus mobility using my new mat and foam roller from Evoke, exclusively @sportchek. This mat is nice and plush which is a must when rolling on your spine as we do in much of the mat pilates repertoire! This roller has graphics to demonstrate some different exercises and rolling techniques should you need some inspiration and to keep your routine simple! I’ve added a few more ideas in this video 😊 Check out the full Evoke assortment at your local SportChek store or online. 

**note this video is sped up X3**
